      "title": "140,000 LP Gas Cylinders to the market today (28)",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); Litro Gas said that 140,000 cooking gas cylinders will be distributed to the market today (28).",
        "The Chairman of Litro Muditha Peiris said that several more gas shipments are scheduled to reach the country in the next week.",
        "The Chairman further said that steps have been taken to issue LP Gas cylinders through gas dealerships and distributors."
